quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  47,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  47,1,jin logon ne kufar kiya aur ( ouron ko ) khuda ke raste se roka. khuda ne un ke aamaal barbaad kar diye
  47,2,aur jo imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay aur jo ( kitaab ) Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam par nazil hui usay mantay rahay aur woh un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se brhq hai un se un ke gunah daur kardiye aur un ki haalat sanwaar di
  47,3,yeh ( habtay aamaal aur islaah haal ) is liye hai ke jin logon ne kufar kiya unhon ne jhooti baat ki pairwi ki aur jo imaan laaye woh apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se ( deen ) haq ke peechay chalay. isi terhan khuda logon se un ke halaat bayan farmata hai
  47,4,jab tum kafiroon se bhir jao to un ki gardanein urra do. yahan taq ke jab un ko khoob qatal kar chuko to ( jo zindah pakdae jayen un ko ) mazbooti se qaid karlo. phir is ke baad ya to ahsaan rakh kar chore dena chahiye ya kuch maal le kar yahan taq ke ( fareeq maqabil ) larai ( ke ) hathyaar ( haath se ) rakh day. ( yeh hukum yaad rakho ) aur agar khuda chahta to ( aur terhan ) un se intiqam le laita. lekin is ne chaha ke tumhari azmaish aik ( ko ) dosray se ( ladawa kar ) kere. aur jo log khuda ki raah mein maaray gay un ke amlon ko hargiz zaya nah kere ga
  47,5,un ko seedhay raste par chalaye ga aur un ki haalat durust kar day ga
  47,6,aur un ko bahisht mein jis se inhen shanasa kar rakha hai daakhil kere ga
  47,7,ae ahal imaan! agar tum khuda ki madad karo ge to woh bhi tumhari madad kere ga aur tum ko saabit qadam rakhay ga
  47,8,aur jo kafir hain un ke liye halakat hai. aur woh un ke aamaal ko barbaad kar day ga
  47,9,yeh is liye ke khuda ne jo cheez nazil farmai unhon ne is ko napasandkiya to khuda ne bhi un ke aamaal akart kardiye
  47,10,kiya unhon ne malik mein sair nahi ki taakay dekhte ke jo log un se pehlay they un ka injaam kaisa howa? khuda ne un par tabahi daal di. aur isi terhan ka ( azaab ) un kafiroon ko hoga
  47,11,yeh is liye ke jo momin hain un ka khuda karsaaz hai aur kafiroon ka koi karsaaz nahi
  47,12,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay un ko khuda bahishtoon mein jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain daakhil farmaiye ga. aur jo kafir hain woh faiday uthatay hain aur ( is terhan ) khatay hain jaisay hewan khatay hain. aur un ka thikana dozakh hai
  47,13,aur bohat si bastiyan tumhari bastii se jis ( ke bashindon ne tumhe wahan ) se nikaal diya zor وقوت mein kahin barh kar theen hum ne un ka satyanaas kardiya aur un ka koi madadgaar nah howa
  47,14,bhala jo shakhs apne perwar-digaar ( ki meharbani ) se khulay raste par ( chal raha ) ho woh un ki terhan ( ho sakta ) hai jin ke aamaal bad inhen achay karkay dikhayi jayen aur jo apni khawahishon ki pairwi karen
  47,15,jannat jis ka parhaiz garon se wadakiya jata hai. is ki sift yeh hai ke is mein pani ki nehrain hain jo bo nahi kere ga. aur doodh ki nehrain hain jis ka maza nahi badlay ga. aur sharaab ki nehrain hain jo peenay walon ke liye ( sara sar ) lazzat hai. aur shehad masfa ki nehrain hain ( jo Halawat hi Halawat hai ) aur ( wahan ) un ke liye har qisam ke meway hain aur un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se mughfirat hai. (kiya yeh parhaizgaar ) un ki terhan ( ho saktay ) hain jo hamesha dozakh mein rahen ge aur jin ko kholta howa pani pilaya jaye ga to un ki antadiyon ko kaat daaley ga
  47,16,aur un mein baaz aisay bhi hain jo tumhari taraf kaan lagaye yahan taq ke ( sab kuch suntay hain lekin ) jab tumahray paas se nikal kar chalay jatay hain to jin logon ko ilm ( deen ) diya gaya hai un se kehte hain ke ( bhala ) unhon ne abhikiya kaha tha? yahi log hain jin ke dilon par khuda ne mohar laga rakhi hai aur woh apni khawahishon ke peechay chal rahay hain
  47,17,aur jo log hadaayat Yafta hain un ko woh hadaayat mazeed bkhshta aur parhaiz gari inayat karta hai
  47,18,ab to yeh log qayamat hi ko dekh rahay hain ke nagahan un par aa waqay ho. so is ki nishanain ( wuqoo mein ) aa chuki hain. phir jab woh un par aa nazil hogi is waqt inhen nasiyaat kahan ( mufeed hosakay gi? )
  47,19,pas jaan rakho ke khuda ke siwa koi mabood nahi aur apne gunaaho ki maffi mango aur ( aur ) momin mardon aur momin aurton ke liye bhi. aur khuda tum logon ke chalne phirnay aur tehrnay se waaqif hai
  47,20,aur momin log kehte hain ke ( jehaad ki ) koi sourat kyun nazil nahi hoti? lekin jab koi saaf maino ki sourat nazil ho aur is mein jehaad ka bayan ho to jin logon ke dilon mein ( nifaq ka ) marz hai tum un ko dekho ke tumhari taraf is terhan dekhnay lagen jis terhan kisi par mout ki be hoshi ( taari ) ho rahi ho. so un ke liye kharabi hai
  47,21,( khoob kaam to ) farmabardari aur pasandeeda baat kehna ( hai ) phir jab ( jehaad ki ) baat pukhta hogayi to agar yeh log khuda se sachey rehna chahtay to un ke liye bohat acha hota
  47,22,( ae munafiqo ! ) tum se ajab nahi ke agar tum haakim ho jao to malik mein kharabi karne lagu aur apne rishton ko toar daalo
  47,23,yahi log hain jin par khuda ne laanat ki hai aur un ( ke kaanon ) ko berha aur ( un ki ) aankhon ko andha kardiya hai
  47,24,bhala yeh log quran mein ghhor nahi karte ya ( un ke ) dilon par kufl lag rahay hain
  47,25,jo log raah hadaayat zahir honay ke baad peeth day kar phir gay. shetan ne ( yeh kaam ) un ko muzayyan kar dekhaya aur inhen tole ( Umar ka wada ) diya
  47,26,yeh is liye ke jo log khuda ki aُtari hui ( kitaab ) se bezaar hain yeh un se kehte hain ke baaz kamon mein hum tumhari baat bhi manen ge. aur khuda un ke posheeda mashwaron se waaqif hai
  47,27,to uss waqt ( un ka ) kaisa ( haal ) hoga jab farishtay un ki jaan nikalen ge aur un ke monhon aur pithon par maartay jayen ge
  47,28,yeh is liye ke jis cheez se khuda nakhush hai yeh is ke peechay chalay aur is ki khushnodi ko acha nah samjhay to uss ne bhi un ke amlon ko barbaad kar diya
  47,29,kiya woh log jin ke dilon mein bemari hai yeh khayaal kiye hue hain ke khuda un ke kinon ko zahir nahi kere ga ?
  47,30,aur agar hum chahtay to woh log tum ko dikha bhi dete aur tum un ko un ke cheharon hi se pehchan letay. aur tum inhen ( un ke ) andaaz guftagu hi se pehchan lau ge! aur khuda tumahray aamaal se waaqif hai
  47,31,aur hum to logon ko aazmayin ge taakay jo tum mein larai karne walay aur saabit qadam rehne walay hain un ko maloom karen. aur tumahray halaat jaanch len
  47,32,jin logon ko seedha rasta maloom hogaya ( aur ) phir bhi unhon ne kufarkiya aur ( logon ko ) khuda ki raah se roka aur paighambar ki mukhalfat ki woh khuda ka kuch bhi bigaar nahi saken ge. aur khuda un ka sabkiya karaya akart kardey ga
  47,33,momino! khuda ka irshad manu aur paighambar ki farmabardari karo aur apne amlon ko zaya nah honay do
  47,34,jo log kafir hue aur khuda ke raste se roktay rahay phir kafir hi margaye khuda un ko hargiz nahi bakhshay ga
  47,35,to tum himmat nah haro aur ( dushmanon ko ) sulah ki taraf nah bulaao. aur tum to ghalib ho. aur khuda tumahray sath hai woh hargiz tumahray aamaal ko kam ( aur gum ) nahi kere ga
  47,36,duniya ki zindagi to mehez khail aur tamasha hai. aur agar tum imaan lao ge aur parhaiz gari karo ge to woh tum ko tumhara ajar day ga. aur tum se tumhara maal talab nahi kere ga
  47,37,agar woh tum se maal talab kere aur tumhe tang kere to tum bukhal karne lagu aur woh ( bukhal ) tumhari badniyati zahir karkay rahay
  47,38,dekho tum woh log ho ke khuda ki raah mein kharch karne ke liye bulaye jatay ho. to tum mein aisay shakhs bhi hain jo bukhal karne lagtay hain. aur jo bukhal karta hai apne aap se bukhal karta hai. aur khuda be niaz hai aur tum mohtaaj. aur agar tum munh phero ge to woh tumhari jagah aur logon ko le aeye ga aur woh tumhari terhan ke nahi hon ge
